      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not just a state though. it's the debt. it's millions. there is no \"small step\" that fixes that. i look at the numbers and all i see is a dead end. everyone is waiting for me to figure it out, but i'm just... i'm empty. there is no version of the future where this doesn't follow me everywhere. it feels like the only thing that would actually stop the noise is if i just wasn't here to deal with it anymore.",
